      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPIN AROUND BLUE (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at Taree Super Track in a handy 30.49 beating Pirate Riot. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. SHOWMAN BAZ (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his dynamic 25.97 win at Bulli over 472m. Expecting another bold showing. ZIPPING VIOLET (4) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won two times from three starts. Below best last time at this track (30.16) in a NG, finishing a 8 length fourth. Among the main chances. CYCLONE ETHICS (7) won by a wide margin last start. Must be respected.",
